RVS Random Voting Stage usually occurs at the start of the game and ends around the middle of the first day phase. RVS is used to get the game started by fluffing and randomly voting people. Oh My God You Suck OMGUS stands for "Oh My God, You Suck (for voting for me)!". it is sometimes used as a shorthand to indicate that you are voting for someone primarily because they voted for you. It is a behavior often associated with inexperienced players. PoE Process of Elimination A strategy which attempts to identify townies instead of scum, so that the scum can be "POE'ed"/found by lynching from amongst the uncleared players.
